reviewText: By far the best Alaska hunting DVDs available. Content is real, real Alaskan Trophies are harvested and Billy Molls is the real deal, no Hollywood producing, just real awesome hunting footage that all hunters want to see!

If you have watched season 1 of the Modern Day Mountain Man and enjoyed every hunt, season 2 only gets better. The thrill of the hunt and the satisfaction of the clients is undescribable and will have you wanting the next 2 seasons. Can not say enough about these videos!
